info.title: librarymanagementsystem-payment-service API
info.description: Handles overdue fee assessment, payment resolution (member and staff), Stripe integration, fee/payment audit trail, and payment oversight for the Smart Library Management System.

Bearer.description:
JWT Authorization header using the Bearer scheme. 

 
  Enter 'Bearer' [space] and then your token in the text input below.
                      

Example: 'Bearer 12345abcdef'
